#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:2
msgid "沙箱"
msgstr "Sandbox"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:5
msgid "常用函数"
msgstr "Common Functions"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:6
msgid "eval / exec / compile"
msgstr "eval / exec / compile"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:7
msgid "dir / type"
msgstr "dir / type"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:8
msgid "globals / locals / vars"
msgstr "globals / locals / vars"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:9
msgid "getattr / setattr"
msgstr "getattr / setattr"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:12
msgid "导入包方式"
msgstr "Package Import Methods"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:13
msgid "``import os``"
msgstr "``import os``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:14
msgid "``from os import *``"
msgstr "``from os import *``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:15
msgid "``__import__(\"os\")``"
msgstr "``__import__(\"os\")``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:16
msgid "``importlib``"
msgstr "``importlib``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:17
msgid "``imp``"
msgstr "``imp``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:18
msgid "``reload(os)``"
msgstr "``reload(os)``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:19
msgid "``execfile`` 仅Python2支持"
msgstr "``execfile`` is supported only in Python 2"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:22
msgid "绕过"
msgstr "Bypass"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:23
msgid "``dir(__builtins__)`` 查看内置模块"
msgstr "Use ``dir(__builtins__)`` to inspect built-in modules"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:25
msgid "最简单的思路是在已有的模块中import，如果那个模块中已经 import 可以利用的模块就可以使用了"
msgstr "The simplest approach is to import from an existing module. If that module has already imported a usable module, it can be reused."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:27
msgid ""
"在父类中寻找可用的模块，最常见payload是 ``().__class__.__bases__[0].__subclasses__()`` "
"或者用魔术方法获取全局作用域 ``__init__.__func__.__globals__``"
msgstr ""
"Look for usable modules in parent classes. The most common payload is "
"``().__class__.__bases__[0].__subclasses__()``, or use magic methods to obtain "
"the global scope through ``__init__.__func__.__globals__``."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:29
msgid ""
"有些网站没有过滤 pickle 模块，可以使用 pickle 实现任意代码执行，生成 payload 可以使用 "
"``https://gist.github.com/freddyb/3360650``"
msgstr ""
"Some sites do not filter the pickle module. In that case, pickle can be used "
"to achieve arbitrary code execution. Payloads can be generated with "
"``https://gist.github.com/freddyb/3360650``."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:31
msgid "有的沙箱把相关的模块代码都被删除了，则可以使用libc中的函数，Python 中调用一般可以使用 ctypes 或者 cffi。"
msgstr "If a sandbox removes the relevant module code, functions in libc can be used instead. In Python, they are usually called through ctypes or cffi."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:33
msgid "``\"A\"\"B\" == \"AB\"``"
msgstr "``\"A\"\"B\" == \"AB\"``"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:36
msgid "防御"
msgstr "Defense"

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:37
msgid "Python官方给出了一些防御的建议"
msgstr "The official Python documentation provides several defensive suggestions."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:39
msgid "使用Jython并尝试使用Java平台来锁定程序的权限"
msgstr "Use Jython and try to restrict program permissions through the Java platform."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:40
msgid "使用fakeroot来避免"
msgstr "Use fakeroot to reduce impact."

#: ../../source/language/python/sandbox.rst:41
msgid "使用一些rootjail的技术"
msgstr "Use rootjail techniques."
